{#
Meeting minutes template.

Generates formal meeting minutes with:
- Meeting details
- Attendees
- Agenda items
- Discussion points
- Action items

Required context:
- title: Meeting title
- summary: Object with short, medium, long summaries

Optional context:
- date: Meeting date
- time: Meeting time
- location: Meeting location (or "Virtual")
- attendees: List of attendee names
- chapters: List of agenda items/topics
- highlights: List of key discussion points
- action_items: List of action items with assignee and due date
- next_meeting: Next meeting date/time
#}

